name: bro
description: The history of marijuana can be seen in many countries, in legends and even in the Bible. Everyone uses it in their own way. And it’s also used in different ways. Someone just wanna looks cool and buys different types of bongs. Someone smokes through a pipe like Pablo Escobar, but I think if Bob Marley lived in Russia, he would be smoking pot through a leaky plastic bottle, because there’s nothing more aesthetic like a homemade appliance and a dirt access. So respect Bob Marley. But the important thing is not to overdo the stuff. Be careful!
